description:
Get motivation to quit smoking and get healthier - with Keep Calm & Quit Smoking. 

=======Let's start your way to a healthy life!=========
- First, enter your personal information;
- Then type the number of cigarettes smoked per day;
- Enter the price of one cigarette pack and the number of cigarettes in one pack;
- Also choose the currency;
- You can choose the start day of counting;
- Press Start to start statistics counting.

============View detailed statistics===============
- Time spent without smoking cigarettes;
- Saved money;
- The number of cigarettes smoked if you didn't quit smoking;
- Approximate increase in life expectancy.
Press Share and tell your friends how well you are doing!

==========Get various achievements==============
- Health;
- Time without smoking;
- Number of cigarettes you didn't smoke;
- Saved money.

==============More functions==================
- Get great advices to quit smoking faster;
- See how your health is improving with a special table;
- Change the settings, restart the app and get new stats.

Addiction to Alcohol is Hard and consuming. Want to self help and quit? Need support and tips? This is App for you. 
You will find intuitive facts and truth, everyday tips, overcoming video lessons that bring you support, and motivational quotes to maintain your spiritual strength. This app is your solution.

Why THIS application is different:

- Intuitive Facts and Truth: Brief you what is the symptom, what is the cause and effect;
- Everyday Tips:  Solutions that come in handy anytime, anywhere;
- Best Overcoming Video Lessons: Provide the successful experiences and the latest solutions, mentally and clinically and more; 
- Motivational Quotes: Spiritual Support Everyday

This app is perfect tool for those who seek help to quit, and those who want to help family or friends to quit.

We look forward your feedback and comment to improve your experience with this application.

